Interface JCasTermAnnotator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.uima.analysis_component.AnalysisComponent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJCasTermAnnotator, DefaultJCasTermAnnotator, OverlapJCasTermAnnotator

    public interface JCasTermAnnotator
extends org.apache.uima.analysis_component.AnalysisComponent
    An annotator that looks up dictionary terms in text using RareWordDictionary s and adds them as entities to the Cas using a TermConsumer Author: SPF Affiliation: CHIP-NLP Date: 2/24/14
